Package com.intel.jndn.utils

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Cancellation
    Represents a token used for canceling some ongoing action.
    Client
    Base functionality provided by all NDN clients in this package.
    ContentStore
    Represents a named content store of NDN data which allows querying by name or interest; TODO merge with Repository
    NameTree<T>
    Represent a tree of nodes, branching based on their component values
    On<T>
    Generic callback API for receiving some signal T when an event is fired.
    PendingInterestTable
    Represent a pending interest table; the jndn net.named_data.jndn.impl.PendingInterestTable depended on several patterns such as List output parameters for collecting output and did not allow querying without extracting (see PendingInterestTable.has(Interest)).
    ProcessingStage<T,Y>
    Provide a generic API for processing Interest and Data packets; e.g.
    Publisher  
    Repository
    Define API for storing and retrieving NDN packets
    Server
    Base interface for defining a server; see descendant interfaces for different modes of serving packets.
    Subscriber  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Topic
    A publish-subscrib topic; see the pubsub package for implementation details
